<div class="upsell-wrapper">
  <div class="upsell-modal">
    <div class="modal-close">
      <a href="#" class="close-upsell">X</a>
   	</div>
    <strong>DON'T FORGET THE STOCKING STUFFERS!</strong>
    <p>Weâ€™ve gathered some of our favorite stocking stuffers for this holiday season. Get some before it is too late!</p>
    <ul class="upsell-grid">
    {% comment %}
